    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sound example of Bavarian engineering, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis maintains its precision through a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry, with recent service addressing the critical valve clearance adjustments and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The subframe has been inspected and remains structurally sound. A true driver\u2019s car, this M3 offers a tactile connection to the road with the performance headroom expected of the E46 platform.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
