    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained executive sedan that perfectly balances luxury and performance. The exterior features a deep metallic finish that retains a brilliant shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel\u2014typical for a vehicle that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any tears, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster. All technological features, including the navigation system, dual-zone climate control, and the premium surround-sound audio, are fully functional. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, ensuring the turbocharged engine delivers smooth power and the transmission shifts seamlessly. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has been cared for by a non-smoker and kept in a climate-controlled garage. It offers a sophisticated driving experience for its next owner without the price tag of a showroom-new model.",
